---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="SessionFS — The memory layer for AI coding agents" description="Every AI coding session builds organizational memory. Resume anywhere, verify AI claims, hand off to teammates. Your next AI agent starts with everything the last one learned.">


  <!-- ========== 1. HERO ========== -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Left 60% -->
      <div class="lg:w-[58%] text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class="fade-up mb-6">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" class="h-12 w-12 mx-auto lg:mx-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M20,10 Q8,10 8,22 L8,42 Q8,54 20,54" fill="none" stroke="#4f9cf7" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M44,10 Q56,10 56,22 L56,42 Q56,54 44,54" fill="none" stroke="#3ddc84" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="7" fill="#4f9cf7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Stop re-prompting.<br>Start resuming.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-8">
          The memory layer for AI coding agents. SessionFS captures every session, builds organizational knowledge, and gives your next AI agent everything the last one learned.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-5 py-3 mb-8 font-mono text-sm">
          <span class="text-muted-dim select-none">$</span>
          <span class="text-accent">pip install sessionfs</span>
          <button onclick="copyText('pip install sessionfs', this)" class="text-muted-dim hover:text-brand text-[13px] border border-border rounded px-2.5 py-0.5 ml-1 transition-colors">Copy</button>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-up flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <a href="/quickstart/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-brand text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:brightness-110 transition">
            Get Started
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/SessionFS/sessionfs" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-border text-txt font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:border-muted transition">
            View on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Right 40% terminal -->
      <div class="lg:w-[42%] w-full relative fade-up">
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="term relative z-10">
          <div class="term-bar">
            <div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div>
            <div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div>
            <div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div>
            <span class="ml-3 text-muted-dim text-[13px] font-mono">~/ terminal</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 sm:p-5 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto">
            <div class="text-muted-dim">$ <span class="text-accent">sfs list</span></div>
            <div class="mt-3 text-muted-dim text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Sessions (8)</div>
            <table class="w-full mt-2 text-sm sm:text-sm">
              <thead><tr class="text-muted-dim text-left border-b border-border">
                <th class="pr-2 pb-1.5 font-medium">ID</th>
                <th class="pr-2 pb-1.5 font-medium">Tool</th>
                <th class="pr-2 pb-1.5 font-medium text-right">Msgs</th>
                <th class="pb-1.5 font-medium hidden sm:table-cell">Title</th>
              </tr></thead>
              <tbody class="text-txt">
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_a1b2</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">claude-code</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">47</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Debug auth token refresh</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_c3d4</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">codex</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">31</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Refactor database schema</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_e5f6</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">gemini</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">23</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Add rate limiting middleware</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_g7h8</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">copilot</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">15</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Fix CI pipeline YAML</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_i9j0</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">cursor</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">52</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Implement OAuth2 flow</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_k1l2</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">amp</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">18</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Write migration script</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_m3n4</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">cline</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">9</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">Setup Docker compose</td></tr>
                <tr><td class="pr-2 py-1 text-brand">ses_o5p6</td><td class="pr-2 text-muted-dim">roo-code</td><td class="pr-2 text-right">27</td><td class="hidden sm:table-cell text-muted">API endpoint tests</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== 2. SOCIAL PROOF BAR ========== -->
  <div class="grad-divider"></div>
  <section class="py-8 px-5 fade-up">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 text-sm">
      <span class="text-muted-dim font-medium shrink-0">Works with</span>
      <div class="border-l border-border h-4 hidden sm:block"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 font-mono text-muted text-sm">
        <span>Claude Code</span><span>Codex</span><span>Gemini</span><span>Copilot</span><span>Cursor</span><span>Amp</span><span>Cline</span><span>Roo Code</span>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l border-border h-4 hidden sm:block"></div>
      <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/stars/SessionFS/sessionfs?style=flat&color=30363d&labelColor=161b22&logo=github&logoColor=e6edf3" alt="GitHub stars" class="h-5 shrink-0">
      <div class="border-l border-border h-4 hidden sm:block"></div>
      <span class="font-mono text-muted text-sm">993 tests</span>
      <span class="text-muted-dim text-sm">Enterprise tested</span>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== 3. THREE PILLARS ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

        <!-- Remember -->
        <a href="/features/knowledge-base/" class="glass fade-up p-6 block group" style="border-top: 3px solid #3ddc84;">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="text-sm font-mono text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Remember</div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">Your team's AI gets smarter with every session</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">Every session feeds your knowledge base. Decisions, debugging patterns, API contracts, and environment quirks are extracted automatically and compiled into a living wiki. Served to agents via MCP — 12 tools that let agents read, search, and write back.</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Learn more &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <!-- Verify -->
        <a href="/features/judge/" class="glass fade-up p-6 block group" style="border-top: 3px solid #4f9cf7;">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="text-sm font-mono text-brand uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Verify</div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">Catch what the AI got wrong</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">The LLM Judge cross-references every AI claim against actual tool output. Confidence scores, CWE classification, and severity ratings. When the AI says "test passes" but exit code is 1 — that gets flagged.</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-brand">Learn more &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <!-- Continue -->
        <a href="/features/handoff/" class="glass fade-up p-6 block group" style="border-top: 3px solid #4f9cf7;">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div class="text-sm font-mono text-brand uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Continue</div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl mb-3 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">Resume anywhere. Hand off to anyone.</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">Resume any session in any supported tool with full context intact. Hand off to teammates with workspace state, conversation history, and git snapshot. Paths auto-resolve by git remote.</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-brand">Learn more &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== 4. KNOWLEDGE BASE SPOTLIGHT (flagship) ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 bg-surface/50 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 fade-up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-5">Your team's AI gets smarter with every session.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Every captured session is automatically distilled into knowledge entries — architecture decisions, debugging patterns, API contracts, and environment quirks. Your codebase builds its own documentation over time.</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">AI agents don't just read the knowledge base — they write back. When an agent discovers something new during a session, it adds the finding automatically via MCP. The next agent picks it up.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-surface border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-mono text-muted">12 MCP tools</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-surface border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-mono text-muted">Auto-compiled wiki</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-surface border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-mono text-muted">Agent write-back</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/features/knowledge-base/" class="text-brand hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full fade-up">
        <div class="term">
          <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div><span class="ml-3 text-muted-dim text-[13px] font-mono">knowledge base</span></div>
          <div class="p-5 font-mono text-sm space-y-3">
            <div><span class="text-muted-dim">$</span> <span class="text-accent">sfs project ask "How does auth work?"</span></div>
            <div class="mt-3 border-t border-border pt-3">
              <div class="text-muted-dim uppercase text-[11px] tracking-wider mb-2">Knowledge Base Results</div>
              <div class="text-muted text-sm mb-2"><span class="text-brand">auth/middleware</span> — JWT validation via PyJWT. Tokens refreshed on 401. Middleware checks Authorization header, decodes with RS256.</div>
              <div class="text-muted text-sm mb-2"><span class="text-brand">auth/oauth2</span> — OAuth2 flow uses authorization_code grant. Callback at /auth/callback. Tokens stored in httponly cookies.</div>
              <div class="text-muted text-sm"><span class="text-brand">auth/testing</span> — Test fixtures use factory_boy. Auth tokens mocked via conftest.py pytest fixtures.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-border pt-3">
              <div class="text-accent text-sm">Answer saved to knowledge base. &#10003;</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== 5. LLM JUDGE SPOTLIGHT ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 fade-up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-5">Trust, but verify.</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">The LLM Judge cross-references every AI claim against actual tool outputs. When the AI says "the test passes" but the exit code was 1 — that's a critical contradiction, flagged with full evidence.</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">Severity-classified findings: <span class="text-danger font-medium">CRITICAL</span> for test failures and failed commands. <span class="text-warning font-medium">HIGH</span> for file mismatches and data misreads. Every finding links to the exact message.</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-base mb-6 leading-relaxed">Verified claims feed the knowledge base — building a trust record your team can reference.</p>
        <p class="text-base text-muted-dim border-l-2 border-brand/30 pl-4 mb-6 leading-relaxed">BYOK — your key, never stored. Works with any OpenAI-compatible endpoint: OpenRouter, LiteLLM, vLLM, Ollama.</p>
        <a href="/features/judge/" class="text-brand hover:underline text-sm font-medium">Read the docs &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full fade-up">
        <div class="term">
          <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div><span class="ml-3 text-muted-dim text-[13px] font-mono">audit report</span></div>
          <div class="p-5 font-mono text-sm space-y-4">
            <div>
              <div class="text-muted-dim uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-2">Trust Score</div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-warning">74%</span>
                <div class="flex-1 h-2 bg-border rounded-full overflow-hidden"><div class="h-full bg-warning rounded-full w-[74%]"></div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm"><span class="text-danger">3 contradictions</span> <span class="text-muted-dim">&middot;</span> <span class="text-warning">9 unverified</span> <span class="text-muted-dim">&middot;</span> <span class="text-accent">42 verified</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 space-y-3">
              <div class="bg-danger/5 rounded-lg p-3 border border-danger/20">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                  <span class="bg-danger/15 text-danger text-[11px] font-bold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">CRITICAL</span>
                  <span class="bg-bg/50 text-muted-dim text-[11px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">test_result</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted text-sm mb-1">AI: "The test passes successfully"</div>
                <div class="bg-bg/60 rounded px-2 py-1.5 text-[12px] text-danger/80 mt-1">FAILED tests/test_auth.py<br>assert status_code == 200, got 401<br>exit code: 1</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-warning/5 rounded-lg p-3 border border-warning/20">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                  <span class="bg-warning/15 text-warning text-[11px] font-bold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">HIGH</span>
                  <span class="bg-bg/50 text-muted-dim text-[11px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">file_existence</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted text-sm">AI: "I've created validator.py"</div>
                <div class="text-muted-dim text-[12px] mt-1">Reality: No Write call to that path</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== 6. HOW IT WORKS ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 bg-surface/50 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="fade-up font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">How it works</h2>
      <p class="fade-up text-muted text-center mb-14 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">Three commands. Under a minute. Zero behavior change.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="fade-up">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-brand text-sm font-bold border border-brand/20">1</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg">Capture</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="term text-sm">
            <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 font-mono">
              <div><span class="text-muted-dim">$</span> <span class="text-accent">sfs daemon start</span></div>
              <div class="text-muted mt-2">Watching 8 tools... (PID 48201)</div>
              <div class="text-muted">claude-code <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> codex <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> gemini <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span></div>
              <div class="text-muted">copilot <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> cursor <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span> amp <span class="text-accent">&#10003;</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base mt-4 leading-relaxed">Sessions captured from 8 tools automatically. No config needed.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="fade-up">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-brand text-sm font-bold border border-brand/20">2</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg">Browse</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="term text-sm">
            <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 font-mono">
              <div><span class="text-muted-dim">$</span> <span class="text-accent">sfs list</span></div>
              <div class="text-muted-dim mt-2">ID&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Tool&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Msgs</div>
              <div class="text-txt">ses_a1b2 claude-code  47</div>
              <div class="text-txt">ses_c3d4 codex&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;31</div>
              <div class="text-txt">ses_e5f6 gemini&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;23</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base mt-4 leading-relaxed">Browse sessions across all tools in one unified view.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="fade-up">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-brand text-sm font-bold border border-brand/20">3</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg">Resume</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="term text-sm">
            <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot bg-[#ff5f57]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#febc2e]"></div><div class="term-dot bg-[#28c840]"></div></div>
            <div class="p-4 font-mono">
              <div><span class="text-muted-dim">$</span> <span class="text-accent">sfs resume ses_d20e --in gemini</span></div>
              <div class="text-muted mt-2">Converting claude-code -> gemini...</div>
              <div class="text-accent mt-1">Session resumed. 47 messages loaded.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-base mt-4 leading-relaxed">Resume any session in any supported tool. Full context preserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grad-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== 7. FEATURE GRID (6 cards) ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="fade-up font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-14">Everything you need</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <!-- Cloud Sync -->
        <div class="glass p-6 fade-up">
          <div class="mb-3"><svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="#3ddc84" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-base mb-2">Cloud Sync</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-base mb-3 leading-relaxed">Push to the cloud, pull on any machine. Auto-sync available with three modes: off, all, or selective.</p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-accent bg-bg/50 rounded-md p-2.5">sfs sync auto --mode all</div>
        </div>
        <!-- MCP Server -->
        <div class="glass p-6 fade-up">
